  "prompt": "How can we find people on WhatsApp without their phone number?",
  "response": "Finding people on WhatsApp without their phone number is not possible. WhatsApp is designed to connect people using their phone numbers as identifiers. This ensures the privacy and security of its users, as you can only communicate with people whose phone numbers you have. The platform does not provide any features or tools to search for users without knowing their phone numbers first.\n\nIf you need to connect with someone, consider asking them directly for their phone number or finding other ways to contact them initially, such as through social media, email, or mutual contacts.",
